<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>California Natural Hazard Disclosure Statement</title>
  <style>
    /* --- Typography & Layout --- */
    html, body { margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 30px; }
    h1 { text-align: center; font-size: 18px; text-transform: uppercase; margin: 0 0 12px; }
    .section-title { font-weight: bold; margin-top: 24px; font-size: 15px; }
    .muted { color:#666; font-size:12px; margin-top:6px; }

    /* --- Tables --- */
    table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 12px; table-layout: fixed; }
    th, td { text-align: left; vertical-align: top; padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #000; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; }
    .hazard-matrix th { background: #f7f7f7; }

    /* Fit matrix to one page */
    .hazard-matrix { font-size: 12px; }
    .hazard-matrix th, .hazard-matrix td { padding: 6px; }
    .hazard-matrix td:nth-child(1),
    .hazard-matrix td:nth-child(3),
    .hazard-matrix td:nth-child(5) { width: 22px; }

    /* NHDS official form styling */
    .nhds-form { font-size: 13px; padding: 60px 0 36px; }
    .nhds-form-continued { font-size: 13px; padding: 60px 0 36px; }
    .hazard-block.liquefaction { margin-top: 16px; padding-top: 0; }
    .nhds-signoff { margin-top: 26px; }
    .nhds-form h1 { font-size: 18px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .nhds-intro { margin: 8px 0; }
    .nhds-paragraph { margin: 10px 0; }
    .form-blank { display: inline-block; min-width: 110px; border-bottom: 1px solid #000; padding: 2px 6px; background: #e6edff; }
    .form-blank.short { min-width: 90px; }
    .form-blank.address { min-width: 320px; }
    .hazard-block { margin-top: 16px; page-break-inside: avoid; break-inside: avoid; }
    .hazard-block p { margin: 0; }
    .hazard-options { margin-top: 6px; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px 32px; }
    .form-choice { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; font-size: 13px; padding: 2px 4px; }
    .form-choice.long { flex-basis: 100%; padding: 2px 4px; }
    .choice-highlight { background: #e6edff; border-radius: 3px; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; }
    .form-choice.long { flex-basis: 100%; }
    .checkbox {
      width: 18px;
      height: 18px;
      border: 1px solid #000; 
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: #fff;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1;
      color: transparent;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI Symbol', Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    .checkbox::after {
      content: "";
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .checkbox.checked {
      border-color: #000;
      color: #000;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .checkbox.checked::after {
      content: "\2714";
      color: #000;
    }
    /* --- Page & Flow Controls --- */
    .page {
      position: relative;
      page-break-after: always;
      padding: 40px 0 72px; /* reserve space for fixed footer */
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    .cover { text-align: center; page-break-after: always; }
    .cover img.logo { height: 200px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .cover-footer { margin-top: 28px; font-size: 12px; color: #666; }

    tr, td, th { page-break-inside: avoid; }
    p, div { page-break-inside: auto; }

    .disclaimer { font-size: 12px; margin-top: 18px; }
    .signature-block { margin-top: 22px; text-align: left; }
    .signature-block label { display: block; margin-top: 10px; }
    .signature-pad { border: 1px solid #ccc; width: 300px; height: 80px; margin-top: 4px; }

    /* SOURCES and CONTACT page rules */
    .sources-page {
      page-break-before: always;
      page-break-after: always;  /* legacy */
      break-after: page;          /* modern */
      font-size: 13px;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }
    .sources-page ul { margin-top: 10px; line-height: 1.6; padding-left: 18px; }
    .sources-page h1 { font-size: 15px; text-transform: uppercase; }

    .contact-page {
      page-break-before: always;
      break-before: page;
      font-size: 13px;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }
    .disclaimer-page {
      page-break-before: always;
      break-before: page;
    }
    .contact-page ul { margin-top: 10px; line-height: 1.6; padding-left: 18px; }

    .footer {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 20px;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      text-align: right;
      width: 95%;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #555;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    /* Appendix & Addendum styling */
    .appendix { page-break-before: always; }
    .appendix h1 { margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 18px; text-transform: uppercase; }
    .appendix .intro { color:#333; font-size:13px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .appendix .ai-note { font-size: 12px; margin-top: 10px; }
    .ai-validation { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold; color: #333; margin: 8px 0; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .ai-validation.muted { color: #555; font-weight: normal; }
    .ai-validation .ai-validation-label { white-space: nowrap; }
    .ai-validation .ai-validation-badge { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
    .ai-validation .ai-validation-badge svg,
    .ai-validation .ai-validation-badge img { height: 18px; width: auto; }
    .ai-validation .ai-validation-badge img { display: block; }
    .appendix .ai-validation { margin-top: 12px; }
    .appendix .ai-validation .ai-validation-seal { font-size: 14px; }
    .appendix table { font-size: 12px; } /* Smart-Verify matrix font size */
    /* Hazard map page */
    .hazard-map-page { page-break-before: always; break-before: page; }
    .hazard-map-page h2 { font-size: 18px; text-transform: uppercase; margin: 0 0 16px; }
    .hazard-map-container { position: relative; margin: 18px 0; }
    .hazard-map-container.has-inset { padding-right: 30%; }
    .hazard-map-main { width: 100%; height: auto; border: 1px solid #000; }
    .hazard-map-inset { position: absolute; top: 16px; right: 16px; width: 28%; min-width: 160px; border: 1px solid #000; box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.25); }
    .legend { margin-top: 12px; font-size: 12px; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px 24px; align-items: center; }
    .legend .swatch { display: inline-block; width: 16px; height: 16px; border: 1px solid #000; margin-right: 6px; vertical-align: middle; }
    .legend .swatch.liquefy { background: rgba(255, 138, 0, 0.35); }
    .legend .swatch.parcel { background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.15); }
    .legend .dot { display: inline-block; width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 50%; background: #d0021b; border: 1px solid #000; margin-right: 6px; }
    .hazard-map-page .credits { margin-top: 14px; font-size: 12px; color: #555; }
    .hazard-map-page .hazard-note { font-size: 12px; color: #555; margin-top: 12px; }
    @media print {
      .hazard-map-inset { box-shadow: none; }
      .env-page-header,
      .env-page-header * {
        -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
        print-color-adjust: exact;
      }
    }


    /* NEW: ensure ENV addendum is a separate page & same matrix font size */
    .env-page {
      page-break-before: always;   /* legacy */
      break-before: page;          /* modern */
      padding: 28px 0 36px;        /* balanced vertical buffer */
    }
    .env-page.env-page-continued {
      padding-top: 28px;
    }
    .env-section-group { }
    .env-page-header {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      background: #fff;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      page-break-after: avoid;
      break-after: avoid;
      padding: 0 0 4px;
    }
    .env-page-header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      padding-top: 2px;
    }
    .env-page h1 { font-size: 18px; text-transform: uppercase; }
    .env-matrix {
      font-size: 12px; /* match Smart-Verify matrix */
      page-break-inside: avoid;
      break-inside: avoid;
      -webkit-region-break-inside: avoid;
      -webkit-column-break-inside: avoid;
    }
    .env-matrix-block {
      page-break-inside: avoid;
      break-inside: avoid;
      -webkit-region-break-inside: avoid;
      -webkit-column-break-inside: avoid;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }
    .env-matrix-block.env-low-cost h2,
    .env-matrix-block.env-low-cost h3,
    .env-matrix-block.env-low-cost p > strong {
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    .env-page .env-matrix-block:first-of-type,
    .env-matrix-block.env-matrix-block-first {
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    .env-matrix-block.env-matrix-block-first {
      page-break-before: avoid;
      break-before: avoid;
    }
    .env-retrofit-list { margin: 8px 0 0; padding-left: 20px; }
    .env-retrofit-list li { margin-bottom: 6px; }

    .badge { display:inline-block; padding: 2px 6px; border:1px solid #000; font-size: 11px; margin-left: 6px; }

    /* Hard page-break utility + Terms typography */
    .hardbreak {
      height: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0; border: 0;
      page-break-before: always; /* legacy */
      break-before: page;        /* modern */
      clear: both;
    }
    .sig-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap:12px 24px; }
    .sig-box  { min-height:90px; border:1px solid #bbb; padding:8px; }
    .sig-cap  { font-weight:bold; margin:8px 0 6px; }
    .page-break { page-break-before: always; break-before: page; }
    .terms,
    .terms-continued { page-break-before: always; break-before: page; padding-top: 40px; }
    .terms p { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 10px 0; }
    .terms .section-title { margin-top: 18px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: bold; }

    .terms-list { margin-top: 16px; }

    .terms .terms-heading,

    .terms-continued .terms-heading { font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; margin: 14px 0 4px; }

    .terms .terms-heading:first-child,

    .terms-continued .terms-heading:first-child { margin-top: 0; }

    .terms .terms-sub,

    .terms-continued .terms-sub { font-size: 13px; margin: 4px 0 4px 18px; font-weight: normal; }

    .terms .terms-sub.indent,

    .terms-continued .terms-sub.indent { margin-left: 36px; }



    /* (new) tiny, invisible Zoho Sign text-tag styling */
    .zsign-tag { font-size: 1px; color: #fff; letter-spacing: 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  {%- comment -%} ===== Plan helpers (basic / standard / advanced) ===== {%- endcomment -%}
  {%- assign package_raw = package_type | default: package | default: packageTier | default: bundle | default: reportBundle | default: '' | downcase -%}
  {%- assign package = package_raw -%}
  {%- if package == '' -%}
    {%- if show_env_section -%}
      {%- assign package = 'standard' -%}
    {%- else -%}
      {%- assign package = 'basic' -%}
    {%- endif -%}
  {%- endif -%}
  {%- assign is_standard = show_env_section or (package == 'standard') or (package == 'advanced') -%}

  {%- assign _city_text = city | default: '' -%}
  {%- if _city_text == '' and address -%}
    {%- assign _addr_parts = address | split: ',' -%}
    {%- if _addr_parts.size > 1 -%}
      {%- assign _city_text = _addr_parts[1] | strip -%}
    {%- endif -%}
  {%- endif -%}

  {%- comment -%} ====================== COVER ====================== {%- endcomment -%}
  {% if show_cover or show_cover == nil %}
  <div class="cover">
    <img class="logo"
         src="{{ cover_image_url | default: 'https://static.wixstatic.com/media/39685c_b04a1f9211434ec0b2efe6773e138d94~mv2.png' }}"
         alt="{{ brand_name | default: 'SafeCanopyAI' }}" />

    <h1>
      California Natural Hazard Disclosure Statement
      <span class="badge">
        {%- if package == 'advanced' -%}ADVANCED
        {%- elsif is_standard -%}STANDARD
        {%- else -%}BASIC
        {%- endif -%}
      </span>
    </h1>

    <p class="muted">Reference # {{ report_id | default: "" }}</p>

    {% if is_apn_mode %}
      <p>
        <strong>Parcel / APN:</strong>
        {{ apn | default: "" }}
        {% if tax_apn %}
          &nbsp;&bull;&nbsp;<strong>Tax APN (unit):</strong> {{ tax_apn }}
        {% endif %}
      </p>
      {% if apn_source_line %}
        <p class="muted">{{ apn_source_line }}</p>
      {% endif %}
      {% if apn and tax_apn %}
        <p class="muted">
          APN &amp; Tax APN {% if apn_same_as_tax %}match{% else %}do not match{% endif %}.
          {% if apn_source_line %}{{ apn_source_line }}{% endif %}
        </p>
      {% endif %}
    {% else %}
            <p><strong>Address:</strong> {{ address | default: _full_address | default: full_address | default: "" }}</p>
    {% endif %}

    <p><strong>Report Date:</strong> {{ report_date | default: "" }}</p>
    <div class="cover-footer">For inquiries, see final page</div>
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  {%- comment -%} ====================== MAIN ====================== {%- endcomment -%}
  <div class="page nhds-form">
  <h1>CALIFORNIA NATURAL HAZARD DISCLOSURE STATEMENT</h1>

    <p class="nhds-intro">
      This Natural Hazard Disclosure Statement concerns the real property situated in the City of
      <span class="form-blank short">{{ _city_text }}</span>,
      County of <span class="form-blank short">{{ county | default: "" }}</span>,
      State of California, described as:
    </p>

    {% assign described_address = statement_address | default: property_descriptor | default: property_line | default: address | default: _full_address | default: full_address | default: apn | default: '' %}
    {% assign described_address = described_address | strip %}
    <p class="nhds-intro"><span class="form-blank address">{{ described_address }}</span></p>

    <p class="nhds-paragraph">
      This Statement is a disclosure of natural hazards relating to the above described property in compliance with Section 1102 of the California Civil Code. It is not a warranty of any kind by the seller(s) in this transaction, and is not a substitute for any inspections or warranties the buyers may wish to obtain.
    </p>

    <p class="nhds-paragraph">
      This Natural Hazard Disclosure Statement is made pursuant to Section 1102 of the Civil Code. Other statutes may require disclosures, depending upon the details of the particular real estate transaction (for example: special study zone and purchase-money liens on residential property). In addition, there may be local disclosure requirements in your particular city or county.
    </p>

    <p class="nhds-paragraph">
      The Seller discloses the following information with the knowledge that even though this is not a warranty, prospective Buyers may rely on this information in deciding whether and on what terms to purchase the subject property. Seller hereby authorizes any agent(s) representing any principal(s) in this action to provide a copy of this statement to any person or entity in connection with any actual or anticipated sale of the property. The following are representations made by the Seller based on their knowledge and maps drawn by the state and federal governments. This information is a disclosure and is not intended to be part of any contract between the Buyer and Seller.
    </p>

    <div class="section-title" style="margin-top: 24px;">THIS REAL PROPERTY LIES WITHIN THE FOLLOWING HAZARDOUS AREA(S):</div>

    <div class="hazard-block">
      <p><strong>A SPECIAL FLOOD HAZARD AREA</strong> (Any type Zone "A" or "V") designated by the Federal Emergency Management Agency.</p>
      <div class="hazard-options">
        <span class="form-choice{% if flood_zone == "yes" %} choice-highlight{% endif %}">Yes <span class="checkbox{% if flood_zone == "yes" %} checked{% endif %}"></span></span>
        <span class="form-choice{% if flood_zone == "no" %} choice-highlight{% endif %}">No <span class="checkbox{% if flood_zone == "no" %} checked{% endif %}"></span></span>
        <span class="form-choice long{% if flood_zone == "Do not know and information not available from local jurisdiction" %} choice-highlight{% endif %}">Do not know and information not available from local jurisdiction <span class="checkbox{% if flood_zone == "Do not know and information not available from local jurisdiction" %} checked{% endif %}"></span></span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hazard-block">
      <p><strong>AN AREA OF POTENTIAL FLOODING</strong> shown on a dam failure inundation map.</p>
      <div class="hazard-options">
        <span class="form-choice{% if dam_inundation == "yes" %} choice-highlight{% endif %}">Yes <span class="checkbox{% if dam_inundation == "yes" %} checked{% endif %}"></span></span>
        <span class="form-choice{% if dam_inundation == "no" %} choice-highlight{% endif %}">No <span class="checkbox{% if dam_inundation == "no" %} checked{% endif %}"></span></span>
        <span class="form-choice long{% if dam_inundation == "Do not know and information not available from local jurisdiction" %} choice-highlight{% endif %}">Do not know and information not available from local jurisdiction <span class="checkbox{% if dam_inundation == "Do not know and information not available from local jurisdiction" %} checked{% endif %}"></span></span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hazard-block">
      <p><strong>A VERY HIGH FIRE HAZARD SEVERITY ZONE</strong> pursuant to Section 51178 or 51179 of the Government Code. The owner of this property is subject to the maintenance requirements of Section 51182 of the Government Code.</p>
      <div class="hazard-options">
        <span class="form-choice{% if vhfhsz == "yes" %} choice-highlight{% endif %}">Yes <span class="checkbox{% if vhfhsz == "yes" %} checked{% endif %}"></span></span>
        <span class="form-choice{% if vhfhsz == "no" %} choice-highlight{% endif %}">No <span class="checkbox{% if vhfhsz == "no" %} checked{% endif %}"></span></span>
        <span class="form-choice long{% if vhfhsz == "Do not know" or vhfhsz == "Do not know and information not available from local jurisdiction" %} choice-highlight{% endif %}">Do not know and information not available from local jurisdiction <span class="checkbox{% if vhfhsz == "Do not know" or vhfhsz == "Do not know and information not available from local jurisdiction" %} checked{% endif %}"></span></span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hazard-block">
      <p><strong>A WILDLAND AREA THAT MAY CONTAIN SUBSTANTIAL FOREST FIRE RISKS AND HAZARDS</strong> pursuant to Section 4125 of the Public Resources Code. The owner of this property is subject to the maintenance requirements of Section 4291 of the Public Resources Code. Additionally, it is not the state's responsibility to provide fire protection services to any building or structure located within the wildlands unless the Department of Forestry and Fire Protection has entered into a cooperative agreement with a local agency for those purposes pursuant to Section 4142 of the Public Resources Code.</p>
      <div class="hazard-options">
        <span class="form-choice{% if wildland_fire == "yes" %} choice-highlight{% endif %}">Yes <span class="checkbox{% if wildland_fire == "yes" %} checked{% endif %}"></span></span>
        <span class="form-choice{% if wildland_fire == "no" %} choice-highlight{% endif %}">No <span class="checkbox{% if wildland_fire == "no" %} checked{% endif %}"></span></span>
        <span class="form-choice long{% if wildland_fire == "Do not know" or wildland_fire == "Do not know and information not available from local jurisdiction" %} choice-highlight{% endif %}">Do not know and information not available from local jurisdiction <span class="checkbox{% if wildland_fire == "Do not know" or wildland_fire == "Do not know and information not available from local jurisdiction" %} checked{% endif %}"></span></span>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="page nhds-form nhds-form-continued">
    <div class="hazard-block">
      <p><strong>AN EARTHQUAKE FAULT ZONE</strong> pursuant to Section 2622 of the Public Resources Code.</p>
      <div class="hazard-options">
        <span class="form-choice{% if fault_zone == "yes" %} choice-highlight{% endif %}">Yes <span class="checkbox{% if fault_zone == "yes" %} checked{% endif %}"></span></span>
        <span class="form-choice{% if fault_zone == "no" %} choice-highlight{% endif %}">No <span class="checkbox{% if fault_zone == "no" %} checked{% endif %}"></span></span>
        <span class="form-choice long{% if fault_zone == "Do not know and information not available from local jurisdiction" %} choice-highlight{% endif %}">Do not know and information not available from local jurisdiction <span class="checkbox{% if fault_zone == "Do not know and information not available from local jurisdiction" %} checked{% endif %}"></span></span>
      </div>

    <div class="hazard-block">
      <p><strong>A SEISMIC HAZARD ZONE: LANDSLIDE</strong> pursuant to Section 2696 of the Public Resources Code.</p>
      <div class="hazard-options">
        <span class="form-choice{% if seismic_landslide == "yes" %} choice-highlight{% endif %}">Yes (Landslide Zone) <span class="checkbox{% if seismic_landslide == "yes" %} checked{% endif %}"></span></span>
        <span class="form-choice{% if seismic_landslide == "no" %} choice-highlight{% endif %}">No <span class="checkbox{% if seismic_landslide == "no" %} checked{% endif %}"></span></span>
        <span class="form-choice long{% if seismic_landslide == "Map not yet released by state" or seismic_landslide == "Do not know and information not available from local jurisdiction" %} choice-highlight{% endif %}">Map not yet released by state <span class="checkbox{% if seismic_landslide == "Map not yet released by state" or seismic_landslide == "Do not know and information not available from local jurisdiction" %} checked{% endif %}"></span></span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hazard-block liquefaction">
      <p><strong>A SEISMIC HAZARD ZONE: LIQUEFACTION</strong> pursuant to Section 2696 of the Public Resources Code.</p>
      <div class="hazard-options">
        <span class="form-choice{% if seismic_liquefaction == "yes" %} choice-highlight{% endif %}">Yes (Liquefaction Zone) <span class="checkbox{% if seismic_liquefaction == "yes" %} checked{% endif %}"></span></span>
        <span class="form-choice{% if seismic_liquefaction == "no" %} choice-highlight{% endif %}">No <span class="checkbox{% if seismic_liquefaction == "no" %} checked{% endif %}"></span></span>
        <span class="form-choice long{% if seismic_liquefaction == "Map not yet released by state" or seismic_liquefaction == "Do not know and information not available from local jurisdiction" %} choice-highlight{% endif %}">Map not yet released by state <span class="checkbox{% if seismic_liquefaction == "Map not yet released by state" or seismic_liquefaction == "Do not know and information not available from local jurisdiction" %} checked{% endif %}"></span></span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="nhds-signoff">
      <div class="disclaimer">
        These hazards may limit your ability to develop the real property, to obtain insurance, or to receive assistance after a disaster. The maps on which these disclosures are based estimate where natural hazards exist. They are not definitive indicators of whether or not a property will be affected by a natural disaster. Buyer(s) and Seller(s) may wish to obtain professional advice regarding those hazards and other hazards that may affect the property. Seller represents that the information herein is true and correct to the best of the Seller''s knowledge as of the date signed by the Seller.
      </div>

      <div class="signature-block">
        <label>Signature of Seller:</label>
        <div class="signature-pad">
          <span class="zsign-tag">{% raw %}{{Signature}}{% endraw %}</span>
        </div>
        <label>Date:
          <span class="zsign-tag">{% raw %}{{Date}}{% endraw %}</span>
        </label>

        <label>Signature of Buyer:</label>
        <div class="signature-pad">
          <span class="zsign-tag">{% raw %}{{Signature:Recipient2}}{% endraw %}</span>
        </div>
        <label>Date:
          <span class="zsign-tag">{% raw %}{{Date:Recipient2}}{% endraw %}</span>
        </label>
      </div>

      {%- assign s_size = extra_sellers | size | plus: 0 -%}
      {%- assign b_size = extra_buyers  | size | plus: 0 -%}
      {%- assign max_n = s_size -%}
      {%- if b_size > max_n -%}{%- assign max_n = b_size -%}{%- endif -%}

      {%- if max_n > 0 -%}
        <div class="page-break"></div>
        <h3>Additional Signatures</h3>
        <div class="sig-grid">
          {%- comment -%} Emit anchors that match Zoho role names for extra sellers/buyers {%- endcomment -%}
          {%- for i in (1..max_n) -%}
            {%- if i <= s_size -%}
              {%- assign seller_index = i | plus: 1 -%}
              <div>
                <div class="sig-cap">Signature of Seller {{ i }}</div>
                <div class="sig-box"><span class="zsign-tag">{{ "{{SIGNATURE:Seller" }}{{ seller_index }}{{ "}}" }}</span></div>
                <div style="margin-top:6px;">Date</div>
                <div class="sig-box" style="height:24px;"><span class="zsign-tag">{{ "{{DATE:Seller" }}{{ seller_index }}{{ "}}" }}</span></div>
              </div>
            {%- endif -%}

            {%- if i <= b_size -%}
